* In January 2024, Lutron Electronics Co., Inc. introduced Maestro dual controls, featuring the innovative LED+ advanced dimming technology.
* In October 2023, Lutron Electronics Co., Inc. introduced the myRoom XC system for the hospitality industry.
* In June 2023, Helvar collaborated with BUCK Lighting to offer smart, energy-efficient lighting solutions.

